How much does it cost?

Excellent practice.

Yes.

Short sentences are very helpful.

Especially for beginners.

Now, let's talk about a repair shop.

Okay.

A mechanic usually works in a repair shop.

The shop can be busy.

Very busy.

Cars come in all day.

