+# Highlights
 
-<!-- Fill in key highlights after reviewing the transcript. -->
+- `Vocabulary Preview`: "Pump iron" is introduced as informal gym language for lifting weights.
+- `Vocabulary Preview`: "Pointers" is explained as another way to say tips, advice, or helpful suggestions.
+- `Dialogue: newcomer at the gym`: The trainer says, "You can always spot the newbies", setting up language for first-time gym users.
