+- `Fluency Builder: I know how it is`: This phrase is explained as a natural way to sympathize with someone else's situation.
+- `Fluency Builder: ripped`: "Ripped" is taught as an informal adjective for someone with a very muscular body.
+- `Discussion: gym habits`: The hosts discuss treadmills, crowded gyms, and going to the gym as a place to exercise and meet people.
+- `Extra practice segment`: The repeated practice section reinforces beginner gym sentences such as "I go to the gym", "I exercise every week", and "I am getting stronger."
